~~~~</p>

<h1 id="put-numbers1format">PUT /numbers/1.format</h1>

<p>Updates number with the given ID.</p>

<p><strong>Resource URL</strong>
@note http://callpixels.com/numbers/1.format</p>

<h1 id="delete-numbers1format">DELETE /numbers/1.format</h1>

<p>Deletes number with the given ID.</p>

<p><strong>Resource URL</strong>
@note http://callpixels.com/numbers/1.format</p>
